('00817201c338', 'Analisis Kebugaran Rohit Sharma oleh Sanjay Manjrekar', 'Sanjay Manjrekar mengungkapkan keyakinannya bahwa kondisi fisik dan performa Rohit Sharma sedang menurun. Penilaian ini menyoroti aspek kebugaran atlet kriket tersebut dalam pertandingan.', 'https://www.hindustantimes.com/ht-img/img/2026/05/29/550x309/jaiswal_rohit_1780031992430_1780031998388_4d418479-8032-43c6-ad1e-c0a52103be6b.jpg', 'umum', 'gnews.io', '[]', 'https://www.hindustantimes.com/cricket/apologise-to-yashasvi-jaiswal-sanjay-manjrekar-tells-selectors-after-rohit-sharma-picked-for-afghanistan-odis-101780031571331.html', '2026-05-29 19:28:47'),
('01a8c7078e80', 'Exercise & fitness', '', 'https://media.post.rvohealth.io/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2021/03/725212-fitness-hub-1200x628-facebook.jpg', 'postur', 'Medical News Today', '[]', 'https://www.medicalnewstoday.com/exercise-and-fitness', '2026-05-12 12:43:37'),
('01cbf794a4dd', 'Perjalanan Penurunan Berat Badan Anandita Sundar: Mengatasi Rumor dan Body Shaming', 'Anandita Sundar membantah rumor Ozempic dan membagikan kisah penurunan berat badannya selama tujuh tahun. Ia juga membahas pengalaman menghadapi trolling, body shaming, dan sorotan publik. Kisahnya memberikan perspektif tentang tantangan perjalanan kebugaran pribadi.', 'https://imgs.etvbharat.com/etvbharat/prod-images/18-06-2026/1200-675-26946229-13-26946229-1781766607052.jpg', 'umum', 'newsdata.io', '[]', 'https://www.etvbharat.com/en/entertainment/khushbu-sundars-daughter-anandita-reveals-truth-behind-her-transformation-talks-about-online-hate-enn26061801356', '2026-06-18 19:18:39'),
('03a2346b5dfc', 'Massive Libyan military exercises ‘a message for our friends and our foes,’ says senior general', '', 'https://smartcdn.gprod.postmedia.digital/nationalpost/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/91f82e503bfaa98bf13364e44ee49e6e559ecbc6-e1779034203243.jpg', 'umum', 'newsdata.io', '[]', 'https://nationalpost.com/news/world/libyan-military-exercises-message-friend-foes', '2026-05-18 04:29:23'),
('05444a258739', 'Sirkuit Latihan ala Spider-Man Disetujui Tom Holland', 'Ingin berlatih seperti Spider-Man? Artikel ini menyajikan sirkuit latihan yang disetujui langsung oleh aktor Tom Holland.', 'https://images.news18.com/ibnlive/uploads/2026/05/Tom-Holland-1-2026-05-7d222282bbbc1bc5ab991ef022647f1b-1200x675.jpg', 'umum', 'gnews.io', '[]', 'https://www.news18.com/lifestyle/health-and-fitness/what-is-cindy-a-look-at-tom-hollands-workout-that-he-swears-by-10159970.html', '2026-06-19 18:32:33'),
('061e609f8693', 'Latihan Pembuka Pinggul untuk Mobilitas dan Kekuatan Otot Kaki', 'Integrasikan latihan pembuka pinggul ke dalam rutinitas mobilitas tubuh bagian bawah Anda. Gerakan ini sangat bermanfaat untuk meningkatkan kekuatan otot pinggul dan glutes, sekaligus memperbaiki fleksibilitas.', 'https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/exyATygFS4yWbNkBtt7g9P-1920-80.jpg', 'umum', 'gnews.io', '[\"Tambahkan gerakan pembuka pinggul ke rutinitas mobilitas tubuh bagian bawah Anda.\"]', 'https://www.tomsguide.com/wellness/fitness/i-train-clients-of-all-ages-and-this-is-the-one-simple-beginner-friendly-exercise-i-use-to-build-hip-strength-and-boost-mobility', '2026-05-29 19:28:47'),
('0666cff688a4', 'This slow ancient practice lowers blood pressure without pills, gyms, or fast walking', '', 'https://cff2.earth.com/uploads/2026/05/16180812/baduanjin-exercise-lowers-blood-pressure.jpg', 'umum', 'newsdata.io', '[]', 'https://www.earth.com/news/slow-ancient-practice-baduanjin-lowers-blood-pressure-without-pills-gyms-or-fast-walking/', '2026-05-18 04:29:23'),
('07d69ec07740', 'Weight Management', '', 'https://www.verywellfit.com/thmb/HHs1oI1YWutV1cvq_0uNVUVCE9M=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Illo_Recipes-4f3c1ba70560483dbaf32698d858aafe.jpg', 'nutrisi', 'Verywell Fit', '[]', 'https://www.verywellfit.com/weight-management-overview-4581837', '2026-05-12 12:43:37'),
